Params: {1: '1', 3: 'You pass through the cluster of Program Ghosts and keeps walking, until an armored protection layer stops you in your tracks.'}
{3: 'A highly complicated data blockade stands in front of a closed space.'}
{3: 'Given the complexity of the blockade, it will probably take you quite some time to deactivate it.'}
{2: 'Lucia', 3: "...We don't have time to go back now. We need to come up with a method to force our way through.", 4: '3'}
{2: 'Lee', 3: 'It seems like it. What should we do?', 4: '2'}
{3: '...The team is looking your way now.'}
{3: 'The space behind becomes accessible as soon as the blockade is deactivated.'}
